Peter Fox arrested at Euston Station in London on suspicion of murders of Bernadette and Sarah Fox . 
  His mother and sister were found dead half a mile apart in Bootle, Merseyside . 
  Mrs Fox died of asphyxiation while her sister was repeatedly stabbed . 
  Police released CCTV images of Peter Fox leaving Liverpool Lime Street on Wednesday night . 
  Body of his sister was found by police on Thursday night . 
  Family of Mrs Fox have said they are 'absolutely devastated'